Ten Random Things About Me:
~i was 10 minutes away from being a c-section =) my mom lucked out
~the one thing that i can NEVER keep organized is my room.
~i've always wanted blue eyes....brown hair and blue eyes is just AWESOME
~i've highlighted my hair ONCE because i got it for free! and they are all grown out! which is good cuz i LOVE my natural hair color.
~i have gremlins living in this house who steal the one item im always looking for...
~i never plan out outfits...whatever happens to be available is what i wear
~ive been know to wake up/shower/get dressed/eat/leave in 8 minutes
~Joe Hahn Is My Cure For The Itch..well no not really... its all about MIKE!
~ me and adam can dance to buglers holiday like NONE other... i've recently develeoped the skill to shimmy thanks to that guy =)
~and like adam..i too bring my lunch to school..and my lunch boxes ROCK

Nine Places I've Visited:
~Oregon
~Washington
~Washington DC =)
~NY, NY
~New Jersey
~Chicago
~Alaska
~Hawaii
~Montana [grrrrrrrr]

Eight Things I Want To Do Before I Die:
~BUY THAT MANSION WITH JESSICA
~Go to Prague
~keep with an exercise routine that gets me all skinny again!
~get kissed in the rain =) yea yea loserish i know
~adams idea was GREAT! go to a concert and go backstage!
~sing in front of people =) NOT including caz cuz they love me no matter how badly i hurt their ears
~learn a foreign language...god i massacre EVERY language im exposed to.. english included...
~ [okay so ive been sitting here for 10 minutes thinking of the last one and im leaving this one for later on]

Seven Ways To Win My Heart:
~be passionate about something.
~make me laugh!
~open minded
~laid back
~show me you care
~remember what i say! its totally the little things
~send me cute little text messages that i recieve in the morning that make me smile and start the day off good =D hehehe

Six Things I Believe In:
~Destiny
~Reincarnation
~Love
~Karma
~you are innocent until proven guilty
~theres good in everyone

Five Things I'm Afraid Of:
~having to struggle to stay alive
~being a loser
~losing face
~losing trust in people
~Getting Hurt.

Four of my Favorite Items in my Bedroom:
~my pillow with my sally pillowcase =)
~my COMPUTER!
~my big fatty Romeo And Juliet on one page
~my fuzzy

Three Things I Do Everyday:
~sleep
~talk
~wonder...

Two Things I Am Trying Not to Do Right Now:
~go back to sleep
~throw up [i feel like junk!]

One Person I Want To See Right Now:
^_^

~What The Hell Are You Waiting For~
